reviewText: If you saw Guys Gone Wild then don't waste your time and money on this one. Some of the same guys are in this one as in the first one with no new guys that I recall. There is a longer shower scene with the cute guy from the first one, but that is it. You don't even get to see the two "big" guys from the first one. I hope this has cured me from buying these "movies".

I own most of the GGW series and have been dis-appointed by many in the series and this is just another example.  While they do a much better job of showing off new and different guys there are 2 "major flaws" in my opinion.  One this is not nearly long enough and is barely 1 hour in full duration and second there are only 2 guys that really get down to business and "get off" for the camera's.  The rest of the movie is just rather blah and rather boring. I def was hoping for "alot" more and was "quite dis-appointed". It's amazing to me that in this series "Hunk Hotel" and "Bad Boys" were so awesome and worth every penny while the rest of the series is very dull and NEED alot more full action from all of the guys not just a couple in the entire movie! My recommendation I would rent this but really don't feel it's worth the 18.00 to own.  We will see what their next "new" release brings next month and I hope it's much better than this OR it might just be the last one I ever buy.  They need longer movies and much more "hard core" action with more guys getting off for us!
